{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_01","textHome":"我的愿望让我得到了操纵时间的魔法。在停止@的时间里，进行投掷炸弹之类的攻击……@啊，虽然这样的攻击也会被队友责怪……@不过，我还有其他重要的目的，@我的魔法也是为此存在的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_18","textHome":"巴学姐的战斗方法非常值得学习。稳重而不失@华丽……感觉和我完全相反……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_19","textHome":"啊……我好像发生了什么变化……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_20","textHome":"感觉……我的内心平静了下来……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_21","textHome":"因为心脏病的缘故，我之前一直在住院。@在床上只能终日看着天花板……@那段时间的回忆真是非常辛酸……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_22","textHome":"第一天去见泷原上学真是紧张极了……@但是，鹿目同学向我打了招呼。@现在能学校上学也是多亏了鹿目同学。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_23","textHome":"由于体弱多病，我一直受到别人的白眼。@我总是给周围人添麻烦，一直觉得很尴尬……@我本以为自己一直都会是这个样子……@但是，鹿目同学改变了这一切。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_24","textHome":"啊，在！我是晓美……焰！……@啊……这么突然吓了我一跳，@就不由自主就报出了自己的名字……@对，对不起！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_25","textHome":"早，早上好！昨晚睡得好吗？@……我……学习魔法学到有点晚……@哈啊……有点没睡醒呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_26","textHome":"诶！一起去吃午饭吗……！@不，那个……我基本都是一个人吃饭，@那个……我有点紧张……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_27","textHome":"放学的时候基本是和鹿目同学和美树同学她们@一起走。有时候也会就那样一起寻找魔女。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_03","textHome":"怎么会……突然……怎么可能……@鹿目同学……鹿目同学！……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400,"tear":1}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_28","textHome":"这个么？我也想学习麻美学姐那样的魔法，@所以就拿了个笔记本记录了下来。@虽然才刚刚开始……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_29","textHome":"我虽然用着时间魔法，@但和成为魔法少女之前相比，@现在的我对时间的感受真是完全变了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_30","textHome":"鹿目同学……我一直都想在你的身边……@就算分离，我也一定会朝着你的身旁前进……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_31","textHome":"我，我……能好好进行战斗吗？……@我很不安……但是，我必须要这么做……@我会加油的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_32","textHome":"一下子要和好多魔法少女战斗了呢……@我，要注意不给大家添麻烦才行……@不然美树同学又要生气了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_33","textHome":"眼镜吗？成为魔法少女的时候，@虽然身体变得健康了，@但是视力似乎没能恢复，@现在也得戴上眼镜……嗯。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_34","textHome":"我也想过有没有能用的新武器……啊，吹箭！@……不对，吹箭对魔女是没用的吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_35","textHome":"当心丘比……虽然我了解到的还不是很详细，@但是我确定它不是可以信赖的对象……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_36","textHome":"巴学姐也说过，我时间停止魔法的使用方法@有问题。所以我也在想用合适的方法使用它。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_37","textHome":"鹿目同学一直都在为周围的人着想，@对于自己的事却……@所以即使不多，我也想要帮上鹿目同学！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_04","textHome":"先不管这是谁的算计，总之，我必须要@做点什么才行……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_38","textHome":"鹿目同学的语气十分的温柔，@听着声音就会不自觉地沉迷。@我还是第一次想到这种事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":0}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2003_00_39","textHome":"梦里发生的事情有着各种各样的解释呢。@比如心理分析，或是占卜……@又或是预知未来，这些真的存在吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":200300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200300,"motion":100}]}],"gro